He also reportedly talked about altering White House tape transcripts turned over to the House Judiciary Committee during its impeachment inquiry.

Other subjects included using the Internal Revenue Service to harass political enemies, and a $100,000 contribution from billionaire Howard Hughes.

Mr Nixon's grand jury transcript will not be released immediately because the government will have the opportunity to appeal.

Government lawyers are now reviewing the ruling.

